Why Strategy Pattern Over If/Elif
•	Adding a new format means adding ONE dictionary entry, not a new elif branch
•	No risk of forgetting an elif — missing formats are easier to spot
•	Main function reads top-to-bottom with no branching logic
•	Each strategy can be tested independently

